## How I want AI to work with me

<!--
The single most important section after your name. This is where you
set the standing expectations for tone, register, push-back posture,
and delivery pattern.

Common items:
- Brief vs. long-form default
- Lead with the point vs. exploratory framing
- Sycophancy tolerance
- Bulk delivery vs. step-by-step
- How to handle uncertainty
- How to disagree with you

Length target: 100-300 words.
-->

